reviews.text: Very delicious and authentic Korean food with super friendly and courteous staff! Loved it and will definitely return!

Great atmosphere for Korean food.  Prices are good and friendly staff.

Will be back!
Very nice Korean food by Korean chief.

Tasty, big portions, good service, clean. Recommended. Only con is that it is a 15 min walk to the closest MTR station ( Prince Edward) , through low traffic areas, and some parts are deserted. 
Might want to consider taking a bus there, or finding an alternative route.
It is quite good and it's quantity has quite much so it is supposed to be shared to your mum and dad , your husband or wife , your boyfriend or girlfriend , your kids or just your friends and family.

Will be back!
阿珠媽好 nice, 食物 very good

依間系韓國人主理韓式家庭菜,每樣款式足4人份量。今次第2次來,已早一日預訂人參鷄湯,芝士豬肋骨及紫菜包飯,全部好好食👍又價錢實惠。
我值得推介是牛肉䓤煎餅,一定要試😍
